headline: HubSpot (HUBS) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of customer platform provider HubSpot (NYSE:HUBS) jumped 4.8% in the morning session after the stock extended its positive momentum as the company highlighted its new AI-driven marketing strategy at its recent investor event, drawing positive reactions from analysts.
